<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 7317(a) establishes the minimum standards an individual must meet in order to qualify for an endorsement as tankerman for various types of oil or hazardous substances.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsection (b) specifies that the tankerman’s endorsement must specify the grades or types of cargo the holder is qualified and allowed to handle.</p>
</note>
